First submission! It's sub-45, so I'm happy about it. It also cuts out 30 deaths from my best runs prior.

We feature some fun things in this run, like screwing up the cutscene skip in Old Site and getting stuck in the ground before the Badeline fight. The only part I'm really unhappy with is the Theo section. I don't even know what I was doing there. Future time save, I guess. Otherwise, general polish and not dying 54 times on accident will help too.

I also don't know what happened between Ch6 and 7 with the video. The audio is still there, but the video has issues. No funny business happened, I swear. Also, apologies for the choppiness at the start and end. Seems to only last for a few seconds, so it's not too bad.
